<template><h1 id="toolbar" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#toolbar" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Toolbar</h1>
<p>Peak adds a hidden toolbar to the top right corner of your screen. It becomes visible when you hover it and it displays the current Tailwind CSS breakpoint (when your env is <code>local</code>). It also has an edit button when you're logged in. The toolbar can be permantly fixed to your window by toggling the button.</p>
</template>
